910
00:56:34,767 --> 00:56:35,977
Allora troviamo Ahtohallan.

911
00:56:37,311 --> 00:56:40,064
Non "noi". Io.

912
00:56:40,231 --> 00:56:40,856
Cosa?

913
00:56:41,023 --> 00:56:43,192
